{"tid":2382102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"油麻地封區｜有居民批政府做戲：試下去封淺水灣丫","createTime":"2021-01-27T05:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T06:48:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"91baffafa86be8f59bf4c49ef6d77d75fcafde65","tid":2382102,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"數名街坊凌晨時一度嘗試離開大廈上班，遭在場警員阻止，有人坐在樓梯等候解封。清晨6時「受限區域」解封，食環署派清潔工到場加強清潔，檢疫人員於大廈各出入口把守，檢查住戶獲發陰性檢測證明信息才准離開，惟因現場尚有部分住戶檢測後仍未收到短訊和二維碼，檢疫人員登記其資料確認住戶已檢疫後亦放行。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居民黎先生約6時獲准離開，他稱，每日凌晨4時出門飲早茶，再到大坑東晨運，認為政府封區阻礙居民生活，批評政府「做戲畀人睇，你試下去封淺水灣丫！」"},{"pid":"bbb7dc6ff4ac89a9170ff608d4fc0a63c8ad3cf3","tid":2382102,"uid":309948,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"居民黎先生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87f15b59899371332707fae2016cd151b1fb60a","tid":2382102,"uid":182653,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:17:18.000Z","msg":"黎先生唔使番工？"},{"pid":"b76ed5a5a38c23bd1b0d99b7cb202a9debfe06d4","tid":2382102,"uid":271516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"有錢人住嘅地方無病毒同病毒六點後<br />\n出現一樣咁神奇"},{"pid":"b53a0918e080ebd46034d55f876eba0353d49cd4","tid":2382102,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cf40058b1982ef1bff80f662ba7cf76d6ffe94","tid":2382102,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>做戲畀人睇，你試下去封淺水灣丫！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a866cf33d2081b5a4f3ec1bf5faeea371c0b017f","tid":2382102,"uid":65952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L07gv89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL07gv89.jpg&h=d4e9bc58&s={SIZ